GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 24th August, 2006
2 Bhadrapada, 1928 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 24th August,
2006 -
Shri K. Chandra Sekhar Rao relinquished the charge of the office
of Minister of Labour & Employment;
i)
ii)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Labour & Employment; and
iii)
Shri A. Narendra relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of State in the Ministry of Rural Development.
(K.L Sharma)
